title: Desert Palace of Mos-Pelaian
story: For many years the palace of Mos-Pelaian remained sealed. Lately a fearsome basilisk has made its home here.

notes.text: A rear entrance into the palace.
A huge gate with a keyhole on the southern wall.
A weird, unnaturally heavy object on a pedestal.
An enormous white crystal, allows a person to breath under water if struck hard.
A cross-shaped key locked in a magical safe.
